## RelationType: 数据规则约束方案

通过 `data_rule.data_type` 匹配 `backup_solution.source_data_type`，将数据侧规则映射到对应的备份方案。

### Endpoint

| Source | Target | Type |
|--------|--------|------|
| data_rule | backup_solution | direct |

### Mapping Rules

| Source Property | Target Property |
|-----------------|------------------|
| data_type | source_data_type |
